Hong iMRO remote diagnosis and operational system, is to be remote equipment maintenance as the core, the whole life cycle of enterprise equipment of health maintenance and guarantee for enterprise safety production equipment operation and maintenance management platform, the platform is based on multidimensional rich data, combined with the traditional diagnosis analysis method, and give full play to the use of big data intelligent technology, timely find analysis positioning equipment running fast and problems in the process of business operations, and user, supplemented by remote assistance diagnosis analysis and efficient tracking Solve problems, aim to improve the management ability of equipment operation and maintenance, save operation and maintenance cost, and create value for the enterprise.

弘讯MRO系统，是弘讯“弘塑云”的一部分，是专为橡塑胶加工行业打造的远程维修维护系统，该系统具备远程维修、远程诊断、远程维护功能，为机械制造厂商、控制系统厂商、销售代理商、塑胶制品生产厂商提供信息共享、资源整合、多方协同的服务平台。此系统以设备远程维护维修为核心，为工厂设备做全生命周期的健康管理，保障企业安全生产；以多维、丰富的数据为基础，结合传统的诊断分析方法，利用大数据AI分析手段，快速及时的发现、定位、解决设备运转过程中的问题；并辅以远程协同会诊，充分交流沟通，高效的跟踪、处理问题，提升工厂设备运维管理的能力，节约运维成本，为企业创造价值。

弘訊MRO系統，是弘訊“弘塑云”的一部分，是專為橡塑膠加工行業打造的遠程維修維護系統，該系統具備遠程維修、遠程診斷、遠程維護功能，為機械制造廠商、控制系統廠商、銷售代理商、塑膠制品生產廠商提供信息共享、資源整合、多方協同的服務平臺。此系統以設備遠程維護維修為核心，為工廠設備做全生命周期的健康管理，保障企業安全生產；以多維、豐富的數據為基礎，結合傳統的診斷分析方法，利用大數據AI分析手段，快速及時的發現、定位、解決設備運轉過程中的問題；并輔以遠程協同會診，充分交流溝通，高效的跟蹤、處理問題，提升工廠設備運維管理的能力，節約運維成本，為企業創造價值。

Techmation MRO system is part of Techmation “tmPlasCloud”. It is a remote maintenance and repair system specially designed for rubber and plastic processing industry. It has remote maintenance, remote diagnosis and remote maintenance functions for machinery manufacturers and control. System vendors, sales agents, and plastic product manufacturers provide information sharing, resource integration, and multi-party collaboration service platforms. This system takes the remote maintenance and repair of equipment as the core, and manages the life cycle of the plant equipment for the whole life cycle to ensure the safe production of the enterprise. Based on multi-dimensional and rich data, combined with the traditional diagnostic analysis method, using the big data AI analysis method, fast Timely discovery, positioning, and solving problems in the operation of equipment; supplemented by remote collaborative consultation, full communication, efficient tracking and processing of problems, improving the ability of plant equipment operation and maintenance management, saving operation and maintenance costs, creating value for enterprises.

Online remote service software put security, fast, efficient and convenient as one of the integration of professional technology and service solutions, close to the needs of users, is a diverse professional and efficient remote service technology platform, for more customers to provide expert services and consultation, enhance the service technology level of equipment manufacturers.
整合各方技术专家，线上协同诊断、技术指导。大数据AI智能分析预测设备故障，及时维修和保养。
整合各方技術專家，線上協同診斷、技術指導。大數據AI智能分析預測設備故障，及時維修和保養。
Integrate technical experts from all sides, online collaborative diagnosis and technical guidance. Big data AI intelligent analysis predicts equipment failures and timely repair and maintenance.

Founded in 1984, Techmation Co., Ltd. was the first to develop a Chinese-displaycomputer controller for injection molding machine in Asia.

We adopts an operating model that integrates both software and hardware in our production of full-computer automatic control systems to fully support machinery industry. maintenance, upgrading and full-scale
integration of machinery.

In 2003, we developed iNet (Injection Molding Machine Premier Network System)to facilitate factory's production and management.

To follow the global trend of energy-saving and carbon reduction, we have beensparing no efforts in the development of HYB (Hybrid Machine Controller).

More than 300,000 units of plastic machine control system have been sold to over 150 customers around the world。 Our system has been the world's most widely used injection molding machine control system,We have set up our service offices in the US, Brazil, Turkey, Iran, India and other countries to provide our customers with the most expeditious and effective terminal services in the world.

In addition to the professional control system for plastic injection machine, we also provide system integration service and control systems for blow moulding machine, extruder control machine, injection blow moulding machine, etc. Moreover, we also deal with industry automation system such as the development of control systems for die casting machine, punching machine, rolling ring machine and so on.

弘讯科技股份有限公司成立于1984年。开发亚洲首部中文萤幕式电脑射出机控制器。持续科技研发技术，服务台湾、中国塑胶业，并全力开展世界竞争力。

以软、硬体一贯作业方式，从事全电脑自动控制系统生产，弘讯科技致力并坚持做机械业最坚实的后盾，从开发、设计、装机、维护、升级到全面整合，给客户最信赖、最有效的服务。2003年更开发网络整合监控系统（iNET），协助塑胶厂生产与车间管理，借由网路连结，管理者(administrator) 可以进行全球营运，提供客户管理新趋势、掌控世界潮流。

『客制化』服务为宗旨，建立长久稳定的客户关系。随技术研发，持续提供客户不断升级的最佳竞争力，是塑胶机产业最有力的控制器系统制造商。

因应全球环保节能、减排趋势，全力开发全闭环油电复合伺服式射出机控制系统(HYB)，弘讯科技始终以产业趋势为导向，做高级机械控制系统制造厂的研发先锋。

创业24年来，塑胶机控制系统全球销售已超过二十万台以上，全球100家以上客户使用，是全球使用率最高的塑胶射出机控制器系统之制造商。近来更致力全球服务据点布局，目前已在美国、巴西、土耳其（伊朗、印度）等地区设立服务处，为塑机客户提供全球性快速、有效的终端服务。

坚持技术研发、市场求新，弘讯公司除注塑机专业控制系统外，也对其他塑机如吹瓶机、挤出机、注吹机等的控制器与系统集成提供新服务，另外在塑胶业以外产业的自动化系统也多所著墨，如压铸机、冲床机、碾环机等的控制系统开拓。

以軟、硬體一貫作業方式，從事全電腦自動控制系統生產，弘訊科技致力并堅持做機械業最堅實的后盾，從開發、設計、裝機、維護、升級到全面整合，給客戶最信賴、最有效的服務。2003年更開發網絡整合監控系統（iNET），協助塑膠廠生產與車間管理，借由網路連結，管理者(administrator) 可以進行全球營運，提供客戶管理新趨勢、掌控世界潮流。

『客制化』服務為宗旨，建立長久穩定的客戶關系。隨技術研發，持續提供客戶不斷升級的最佳競爭力，是塑膠機產業最有力的控制器系統制造商。

因應全球環保節能、減排趨勢，全力開發全閉環油電復合伺服式射出機控制系統(HYB)，弘訊科技始終以產業趨勢為導向，做高級機械控制系統制造廠的研發先鋒。

創業24年來，塑膠機控制系統全球銷售已超過二十萬臺以上，全球100家以上客戶使用，是全球使用率最高的塑膠射出機控制器系統之制造商。近來更致力全球服務據點布局，目前已在美國、巴西、土耳其（伊朗、印度）等地區設立服務處，為塑機客戶提供全球性快速、有效的終端服務。

Description:
1.This programe is to generate customer strings from exists string in old versions.
2.This programe need to run at initialization of the MLM system.
3.After run normally,customer strings can generate from Excel files interpreted from language expert or customer.
4.Only can select one customer to be standard,mostly it is TM(techmation).
5.If moved a version to a customer,when click "Start",all strings of the customer will be cleared and generate again.
6."Mapping" action is to use version AID compare with customer AID.

说明：
1.本程序是从现在有的旧版本里产生客户的特定字串记录。
2.本程序只需要在MLM系统初始化的时候运行。
3.当MLM系统运行正常后，客户字串会从来源于语言专家或客户翻译的Excel文件产生。
4.只能选择一个客户作为标准，一般是TM(techmation)。
5.如果拖动一个版本到客户下，点击“开始”后，客户的所有字串记录会先清空再重新生成。
6.“匹配”动作是用版本AID与客户AID比较。

說明：
1.本程序是從現在有的舊版本裡產生客戶的特定字串記錄。
2.本程序隻需要在MLM系統初始化的時候運行。
3.當MLM系統運行正常後，客戶字串會從來源於語言專家或客戶翻譯的Excel文件產生。
4.隻能選擇一個客戶作為標準，一般是TM(techmation)。
5.如果拖動一個版本到客戶下，點擊“開始”後，客戶的所有字串記錄會先清空再重新生成。
6.“匹配”動作是用版本AID與客戶AID比較。

Techmation MES, an information management system tailored for manufacturing industry, is the preferred solution for smart factories and the cornerstone for enterprises to move towards industry 4.0.  Aiming at the interconnection of information and network of production management elements "human", "machine", "material" and "law" in manufacturing industry, data exchange is carried out. By means of cloud computing and big data analysis, intelligent identification, location, tracking, monitoring and management of production management elements are realized, so as to realize digitalization, informatization and intellectualization of workshop.
弘讯MES系统，专为制造业量身定做的信息化管理系统，是智慧工厂首选解决方案，是企业迈向工业4.0的基石。针对制造行业生产管理要素“人”、“机”、“料”、“法”的信息与网络互连,进行数据交换，通过云计算、大数据分析等手段,实现对生产管理要素智能化识别、定位、跟踪、监控和管理，从而实现车间的数字化、信息化、智能化。
弘訊MES系統，專為制造業量身定做的信息化管理系統，是智慧工廠首選解決方案，是企業邁向工業4.0的基石。針對制造行業生產管理要素“人”、“機”、“料”、“法”的信息與網絡互連,進行數據交換，通過云計算、大數據分析等手段,實現對生產管理要素智能化識別、定位、跟蹤、監控和管理，從而實現車間的數字化、信息化、智能化。

The Techmation MES system is specified designed for the information management system of Machinery manufacturers. It is an intelligent factory first selected solution. It is the foundation stone for an enterprise face to industry 4.0. This system is pointed to "man", "machine", "material" and"method" 4 major production management components's data collection, network interlink, data exchange,  through cloud calculation, Big data analysis, to carry out realtime production management identification, positioning, monitoring and ten realtime production factory digitalize, information and intelligentize.
